{"tid":1589884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸被囚台灣人李明哲喪父　妻子李凈瑜稱願作人質　換李明哲返台奔喪","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:55:21.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2dc80a77d403b840455fe909a5cb6a365a7ef9","tid":1589884,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/limingjit-15_Cynhn_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flimingjit-15_Cynhn_1200x0.png&h=e9c410bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被指煽動顛覆國家政權，2017 年被中國判監 5 年的台灣人李明哲，目前正在中國赤山監獄服刑；她的妻子李凈瑜去信台灣陸委會和海基會，指李明哲的父親 8 月逝世，希望陸委會可以向大陸當局申請，容許李明哲回台灣奔喪，「本人李凈瑜志願於李明哲返台奔喪期間被中國政府監禁當作人質」。<br />\n<br />\n李凈瑜的信件指，李明哲的父親在 8 月 17 日逝世，希望陸委會可以盡快向大陸赤山監獄申請，讓李明哲回台灣奔喪，又希望可以協助她和李明哲的母親一同到監獄探望李明哲；信件特意提及，若李明哲獲准回台，之後都會返回監獄繼續服刑，若大陸當局有疑慮，她願意在這段期間作人質，被中國政府監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%9A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%93%B2%E5%96%AA%E7%88%B6-%E5%A6%BB%E5%AD%90%E6%9D%8E%E5%87%88%E7%91%9C%E7%A8%B1%E9%A1%98%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%AA-%E6%8F%9B%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%93%B2%E8%BF%94%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%94%E5%96%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2593%25B2%25E5%2596%25AA%25E7%2588%25B6-%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2587%2588%25E7%2591%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%25A1%2598%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25AA-%25E6%258F%259B%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2593%25B2%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25A5%2594%25E5%2596%25AA%2F&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK60uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=2f52f9a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25